baby ignore karo ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
baby ignore karo  Example 02 — Variables and Constants
baby ignore karo  Shows yaad (mutable), vada (immutable), and their aliases.
baby ignore karo ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

~~ Mutable variables — can change later
yaad score hai 0
yaad mood hai "romantic"
yaad message hai "tum hi ho meri duniya"

baby bolo na "starting score:"
bolo score

~~ Mutate it — no keyword needed on reassignment
score hai score milan 10
bolo "score after milan 10:"
bolo score

~~ Immutable constants — cannot reassign
vada max_score hai 100
vada author hai "patel krish"
vada heart hai "❤️"

bolo author milan " made this with " milan heart

~~ Human-mode alias: baby yaad rakho = vada
baby yaad rakho piya hai "forever"
baby yaad rakho jannat hai "right here"

baby bolo naa "piya is:"
bolo piya
bolo "jannat is: " milan jannat

~~ yaad_karo is an alias of yaad (natural phrasing)
yaad_karo kadam hai 1
bolo "pehla kadam:"
bolo kadam

love you baby byeee
